蒋超良的45天：从首批专家组抵达武汉到其被去职。
Jiang's 45 days: from the first group of experts arrived in Wuhan until his dismissal.
来源:。
Source:.
经济网						。
Economic Network.
谢玮。
Mr. Xie.
手机扫一扫。
Sweep your cell phone.
字号：。
Brand name:.
《中国经济周刊》记者 谢玮丨北京报道。
China Economic Weekly reporter Xie Wei reports into Beijing.
2月13日，据新华社消息，日前，中共中央决定：应勇同志任湖北省委委员、常委、书记，蒋超良同志不再担任湖北省委书记、常委、委员职务。
Comrade Yingyong has become a member, standing committee member and secretary of the Hubei Provincial Committee, and Comrade Jiang super-liang is no longer secretary, standing committee or committee member of the Hubei Provincial Committee, Xinhua reported.
。
.
同日，马国强不再担任湖北省委副书记、武汉市委书记，王忠林成为新一任的武汉市委书记。
On the same day, Ma Guoqiang ceased to serve as deputy secretary of Hubei Provincial Committee, Wuhan city party secretary, Wang Zhonglin became the new Wuhan party secretary.
。
.
2019年末，新型冠状病毒肺炎疫情从武汉蔓延开来。
Late 2019, the new coronavirus pneumonia epidemic spread from Wuhan.
2019年12月31日，国家卫健委专家组上午抵达武汉，展开相关检测核实工作。
On December 31, 2019, the national health committee experts arrived in Wuhan in the morning to start the relevant testing and verification work.
。
.
从12月31日专家组抵达至2月13日，已有45天。
Forty-five days have elapsed between the Group's arrival on 31 December and 13 February.
《中国经济周刊》记者根据公开报道，梳理了这45天里蒋超良主要的工作安排。
According to a public report, China Economic Weekly has sorted out Jiang's major work schedule for the past 45 days.
。
.
从公开报道看，从12月底到1月20日之前，蒋超良的工作安排集中在湖北省两会及年底的迎新活动上。
According to public reports, Jiang's work schedule from the end of December to the end of January 20 was centered on the CPC in Hubei Province and the welcoming activities at the end of the year.
。
.
12月31日,国家卫健委专家组抵达武汉,正式介入检查核实。
On 31 December, the team of experts of the National Health Commission arrived in Wuhan and formally intervened to check and verify.
武汉卫健委当日通报27例“病毒性肺炎”，未见明显人传人和医护感染。
Wuhan health committee informed 27 cases of "viral pneumonia," no significant human-to-human and medical infection.
。
.
同日，湖北省各界人士迎新年茶话会在东湖梅岭礼堂举行，蒋超良在茶话会上致辞。
On the same day, people from all walks of life in Hubei Province welcomed the New Year tea party held in the East Lake MeiLing Auditorium.
。
.
1月1日，武汉关停华南海鲜批发市场。
On January 1, Wuhan closed the South China Seafood Wholesale Market.
同日，武汉市公安局在其官方微博“平安武汉”发布名为《8名散布谣言者被依法查处》的消息。
On the same day, the Wuhan Public Security Bureau published the official Weibo, "An Wuhan," entitled "Eight people who spread rumors were found and punished according to law."
。
.
1月2日下午，蒋超良主持召开人大常委会第十三次会议。
On the afternoon of January 2, Jiang held the 13th NPCSC meeting.
。
.
1月3日，武汉卫建委当日通报44例“不明显病毒性肺炎”，称未见明显人传人和医护感染。
On January 3, Wuhan Wei Jianjun reported 44 cases of "not obviously viral pneumonia," said no significant human-to-human and medical infection.
。
.
1月3日，蒋超良到湖北省农业农村厅调研“三农”工作。
January 3, Jiang Jiuliang to Hubei Province Department of Agriculture and Rural Research "three agriculture and rural" work.
当日下午，湖北省十三届人大常委会第十三次会议闭会，蒋超良主持并讲话。
That afternoon, the 13th NPCSC meeting of the 13th session of Hubei Province ended.
。
.
1月5日，武汉卫健委当日通报59例“不明原因病毒性肺炎”，称未见明显人传人和医护感染。
On January 5, Wuhan health committee reported 59 cases of "unidentified viral pneumonia," said no significant human-to-human and medical infection.
。
.
1月7日，蒋超良主持省委理论学习中心组集中学习并讲话。
On January 7, Jiang Chaoliang presided over the theoretical learning center group of the provincial Party committee to concentrate on study and speech.
当日下午，蒋超良主持了三个会议，分别是：省委全面深化改革委员会第五次会议，省委军民融合发展委员会第三次全体会议，省委审计委员会第三次会议。
In the afternoon, Jiang held three meetings: the fifth meeting of the Provincial Committee on Comprehensive and Deepening Reform, the third plenary meeting of the Provincial Committee on Civil-Military Integration Development, and the third meeting of the Provincial Committee on Audit.
。
.
1月8日,国家卫健委专家组确认新型冠状病毒为武汉疫情病源。
January 8, the national health committee expert group confirmed that the new coronavirus is the source of the Wuhan epidemic.
。
.
1月8日，蒋超良主持召开省委常委会会议暨省委主题教育领导小组第五次会议。
On 8 January, Jiang held the fifth meeting of the Standing Committee of the Provincial Committee and the Thematic Education Leading Group of the Provincial Committee.
。
.
1月9日，蒋超良主持召开省委民主协商会。
On 9 January, Jiang Chaoliang chaired the Provincial Committee for Democratic Consultation.
。
.
1月11日-17日，湖北省召开两会。
On January 11-17, two conferences were held in Hubei province.
期间无通报新增病例。
No new cases were reported during the period.
。
.
1月11日，武汉卫健委通报41例新冠肺炎确诊，称1月3日后无新感染病人，未发现明显人传人和医护感染。
On January 11, Wuhan Health Commission reported 41 confirmed cases of new crown pneumonia, said no new infections after January 3, no apparent human-to-human transmission and medical infection.
同日，将“不明原因的病毒性肺炎”改称新冠肺炎，病例数由59人减少为41人。
On the same day, the name of "unspecified viral pneumonia" was changed to New Crown Pneumonia, and the number of cases was reduced from 59 to 41.
1月14日，将之前的“未发现医务人员感染，未发现明确的人传人证据”措辞改为“尚未发现明确的人传人证据，不能排除有限人传人的可能，但持续人传人的风险较低”。
On 14 January, the previous wording, "no infection by medical personnel and no clear evidence of human-to-person transmission" was replaced by the phrase "no clear person-to-person evidence has been found, the possibility of limited person-to-person transmission cannot be ruled out, but the risk of continuous person-to-person transmission is low."
。
.
1月11日-17日，湖北省召开两会。
On January 11-17, two conferences were held in Hubei province.
蒋超良主要忙于两会。
Jiang was busy with two meetings.
在此期间，武汉市卫健委均无通报新增新冠肺炎病例。
During this period, Wuhan Health Commission did not report new cases of new crown pneumonia.
。
.
1月18日，湖北省两会闭幕。
On January 18, the Hubei Provincial People's Congress closed.
当日，武汉卫健委通报4例新增确诊。
On the same day, Wuhan Health Commission reported 4 new cases of diagnosis.
。
.
1月19日下午，蒋超良、王晓东到长江水利委员会走访慰问。
January 19 afternoon, Jiang Jiuliang, Wang Xiaodong to the Yangtze River Conservancy Commission to visit condolences.
。
.
同日，蒋超良出席迎新春军地座谈会。
On the same day, Jiang attended the Welcome Spring Army Symposium.
蒋超良、王晓东、马国强等在武汉分别看望慰问部分老同志。
Jiang, Wang Xiaodong and Ma Guoqiang visited some veteran comrades in Wuhan respectively.
。
.
1月21日，蒋超良主持召开省委常委会会议，同日观看文艺演出。
On January 21, Jiang held a meeting of the Standing Committee of the Provincial Committee and watched a cultural performance on the same day.
。
.
1月20日，习近平总书记作出重要指示，湖北武汉市等地近期陆续发生新型冠状病毒感染的肺炎疫情，必须引起高度重视，全力做好防控工作。
On January 20, General Secretary Xi Jinping gave important instructions that pneumonia outbreaks of new coronavirus infections (coronavirus) have recently occurred in Wuhan, Hubei Province, and other places.
李克强总理作出批示要求全力以赴做好防控工作并主持召开国务院常务会议，进一步部署疫情防控工作，要求有力有效遏制疫情。
Prime Minister Li Keqiang issued instructions to make every effort to do a good job of prevention and control and to host a State Council executive meeting to further deploy epidemic prevention and control work, and to effectively contain the epidemic.
。
.
国家卫健委高级别专家组组长钟南山院士证实了新冠病毒的“人传人”，且有医护感染。
Academician Zhong Nan-shan, head of the high-level group of experts on health care, confirmed the human-to-human transmission of the new crown virus.
。
.
1月20日，蒋超良在大冶市走访慰问基层困难群众、困难党员。
On January 20, Jiang visited people in need and party members in need in Daye City.
。
.
同日，武汉市召开新型冠状病毒感染的肺炎疫情防控指挥部工作会议，武汉市委书记马国强出席会议，强调要深入贯彻习近平总书记重要指示精神，落实李克强总理批示要求和国务院常务会议部署，按照省委省政府要求，采取更严格的举措，内防扩散、外防输出，防止疫情扩散蔓延，切实保障人民群众生命健康。
On the same day, Wuhan Municipal Party Secretary Ma Guoqiang attended the meeting, stressing the need to carry out the important directive spirit of General Secretary Xi Jinping, fulfill Premier Li Keqiang's instructions and deploy regular meetings of the State Council.
。
.
1月21日，蒋超良主持召开省委常委会会议，传达学习习近平总书记对新型冠状病毒感染的肺炎疫情的重要指示，以及1月20日国务院常务会议和防控工作电视电话会议精神，研究部署省疫情防控工作。
On January 21, Jiang held a meeting of the Standing Committee of the Provincial Committee to convey important instructions to President Xi Jinping on the pneumonia epidemic caused by the new coronavirus infection, as well as the spirit of the Standing Committee of the State Council and the televised conference call on prevention and control on January 20.
。
.
同日，2020年湖北省春节团拜会文艺演出在武汉洪山礼堂圆满举办，湖北省委书记、省长等领导与全省各界代表一同到场观看演出。
On the same day, the 2020 Hubei Province Spring Festival Gala held in Wuhan Hongshan auditorium successfully, Hubei provincial party secretary, provincial governor and other leaders with representatives from all walks of life to attend the performance.
。
.
1月22日，湖北省启动突发公共卫生事件二级应急响应。
On January 22, Hubei province launched a secondary emergency response to a public health emergency.
。
.
当日，国务院副总理孙春兰在武汉市检查指导新型冠状病毒感染的肺炎疫情防控工作,慰问一线防控人员。
On the same day, Vice Premier Sun Chunlan inspected and directed the prevention and control of the new coronavirus infection in Wuhan city.
。
.
1月22日，湖北省委办公厅省政府办公厅发出通知：省委、省政府成立由省委书记、省长任指挥长的湖北省新型冠状病毒感染的肺炎疫情防控指挥部，并成立专班统筹组织协调。
On January 22, the Provincial Government Office of the Hubei Provincial Commissariat issued a notice: Provincial Party committees and provincial governments set up the Pneumonia Prevention and Control Command for the New Coronavirus Infection in Hubei Province, headed by a provincial party secretary and provincial governor.
。
.
1月22日，湖北省新冠肺炎疫情防控指挥部成立。
On January 22, the Hubei Province Xinguan Pneumonia Prevention and Control Command was established.
。
.
1月23日，武汉“封城”。
January 23, Wuhan "closed the city."
。
.
1月23日上午，蒋超良主持召开省委常委会（扩大）会议暨省肺炎防控指挥部第二次会议。
On the morning of January 23, Jiang hosted the second meeting of the Standing Committee of the Provincial Committee and the Provincial Pneumonia Control Command.
会议强调，要把抓疫情防控作为当前中心工作，全面进入“战时”状态，内防扩散、外防输出，坚决打赢疫情防控攻坚战。
The meeting stressed the need to focus on epidemic prevention and control as the current central task, fully into the "wartime" state, internal non-proliferation, external defense output, resolutely win the battle against the disease.
。
.
当日下午，蒋超良赴武汉市金银潭医院看望慰问战斗在抗击疫情一线的医务工作者，关切了解ICU负压病房患者救治情况，并向医务工作者表示慰问和敬意。
That afternoon, Jiang went to Wuhan Gold and Silver Pool Hospital to visit medical workers fighting the epidemic. He was concerned to learn about the treatment of patients in the ICU negative pressure ward and offered his sympathy and respect to the medical workers.
。
.
1月24日，蒋超良主持召开会商会，调度指挥防控工作时强调，当前，要全力打好疫情外溢歼灭战。
January 24, Jiang Chaoliang chaired the meeting of the Chamber of Commerce, dispatch command and control work stressed that, at present, to play a good outbreak of the spill-out war.
同日，湖北省启动突发公共卫生事件一级应急响应（前一天，浙江、湖南、广东已启动一级响应）。
On the same day, Hubei Province launched an emergency response to a public health emergency (the previous day, Zhejiang, Hunan and Guangdong provinces had launched a first-level response).
。
.
1月25日，蒋超良主持召开省委常委会会议，第一时间传达学习习近平总书记在中央政治局常委会会议上的重要讲话精神。
On January 25, Jiang held a meeting of the Standing Committee of the Provincial Committee to convey, at the first opportunity, the spirit of President Xi Jinping's important speech at the meeting of the Standing Committee of the Political Bureau.
。
.
1月25日，蒋超良主持召开会商会，强调，要坚决贯彻落实党中央国务院关于疫情防控的决策部署，把武汉市作为重中之重，进一步强化措施，全力阻断疫情外溢。
On January 25, Jiang hosted a meeting of the Chamber of Commerce, stressing the need to resolutely implement the decision-making arrangements of the State Council of the Party Central Committee on the prevention and control of the epidemic.
。
.
1月25日下午，蒋超良与王晓东到华中科技大学同济医学院附属同济医院，了解发热门诊接诊救治情况，向坚守在抗击疫情一线的医务工作者表示新春慰问和深切敬意。
On the afternoon of January 25, Jiang and Wang Xiaodong went to Tongji Hospital of Tongji Medical College of Huazhong University of Science and Technology to find out the treatment and treatment of the fever clinic.
。
.
1月26日，湖北省新型肺炎防控指挥部召开会议，对习近平总书记在中央政治局常委会研究新型肺炎疫情防控工作时的重要讲话精神进行再学习、再反思、再贯彻、再落实。
On January 26, the new Pneumonia Prevention and Control Command in Hubei Province held a meeting to re-study, rethink, carry out and implement the important speech of General Secretary Xi Jinping in the study of the prevention and control of the new pneumonia epidemic by the Standing Committee of the Political Bureau.
。
.
1月26日下午，蒋超良到武汉市汉口医院、六医院，调研病房腾退、病床新增情况；随机来到江岸区劳动街光华社区，检查社区防控工作。
On the afternoon of January 26, Jiang went to Hankou Hospital and Six Hospitals in Wuhan City to investigate the evacuation of the wards and the addition of beds.
。
.
1月27日，受习近平总书记委托，国务院总理、中央应对新型冠状病毒感染肺炎疫情工作领导小组组长李克强赴武汉考察指导疫情防控工作，代表党中央、国务院慰问疫情防控一线的医务人员。
On January 27, entrusted by General Secretary Xi Jinping, Li Keqiang, Premier of the State Council and head of the Central Leading Group for the Response to the New Coronavirus Infection Pneumonia, visited Wuhan to guide the prevention and control of the epidemic, representing the Party Central Committee and the State Council.
。
.
1月27日晚，湖北省新型冠状病毒感染的肺炎防控指挥部召开会议，传达学习李克强总理、孙春兰副总理讲话精神和要求，进一步研究部署湖北省疫情防控工作。
On the night of January 27, the Pneumonia Prevention and Control Command for the New Coronavirus Infection in Hubei Province held a meeting to convey the spirit and request of Premier Li Keqiang and Vice Premier Sun Chunlan, and to further study the prevention and control of the epidemic in Hubei Province.
。
.
1月28日，国务院副总理孙春兰率中央指导组听取湖北省疫情防控工作情况汇报，蒋超良、王晓东、马国强等参加会议。
On January 28, Vice Premier Sun Chunlan led the Central Steering Group to hear a report on the prevention and control of the epidemic in Hubei Province. Jiang, Wang Xiaodong and Ma Guoqiang attended the meeting.
。
.
1月29日，国务院副总理孙春兰率中央指导组听取湖北省疫情防控工作情况汇报，研究指导湖北进一步做好医疗资源配置、疑似病例检测、医用物资紧平衡等工作。
On January 29, the Vice Premier of the State Council, Sun Chunlan, led the Central Steering Group to report on the prevention and control of the epidemic in Hubei Province.
。
.
1月29日下午，全省新型肺炎疫情防控调度工作电视电话会议召开。
January 29 afternoon, the province's new pneumonia epidemic control scheduling work video teleconference.
蒋超良出席并强调，要切实把思想和行动统一到习近平总书记重要指示精神上来，落实党中央、国务院决策部署和中央指导组工作要求，加强全省特别是农村地区的疫情防控工作，构筑群防群治的严密防线，坚决遏制疫情扩散蔓延。
Jiang attended the meeting and stressed the need to unify thoughts and actions in the important guiding spirit of General Secretary Xi Jinping, implement the requirements of the Central Committee and the State Council and the work of the Central Steering Group, strengthen epidemic prevention and control work throughout the province, especially in rural areas, and firmly stop the spread of the epidemic.
。
.
1月29日，蒋超良到武汉市检查指导疫情防控工作。
January 29, Jiang Jiuliang to Wuhan City to check and direct the work of disease prevention and control.
。
.
1月30日，蒋超良先后到孝感汉川市、武汉市省中西医结合医院检查指导疫情防控工作。
On January 30, Jiang went successively to Xiaoyan Hanchuan City, Wuhan Province combined with Western medicine hospital inspection to guide the disease prevention and control work.
。
.
蒋超良首次参加新闻发布会。
Jiang attended his first press conference.
。
.
1月30日晚，蒋超良首次参加新闻发布会，鞠躬致哀。
On the evening of January 30, Jiang attended his first press conference and bowed.
。
.
1月31日，蒋超良到黄冈红安县检查指导防控工作。
January 31, Jiang Jiulian to Huanggang Hongan County to check and direct the prevention and control work.
当日下午，蒋超良在武汉市随机检查蔬菜供应、社区防控工作。
That afternoon, Jiang Chaoliang in Wuhan City random check vegetable supply, community control work.
。
.
2月1日，国务院副总理孙春兰率中央赴湖北指导组听取湖北省、武汉市疫情防控重点工作情况汇报。
On February 1, Vice Premier Sun Chunlan led the Central Steering Group to Hubei Province to listen to the state of the epidemic prevention and control in Hubei Province and Wuhan.
。
.
2月1日下午，蒋超良主持召开全省疫情防控调度工作电视电话会议，强调动员一切力量，地毯式搜索疑似病例，快速增加应急救治场所，对所有疑似病人一律先集中隔离，再组织检测、对症治疗，确保应收尽收、一个不漏，严防交叉感染。
In the afternoon of February 1, Jiang hosted a televised conference call for epidemic control and control work in the province, emphasizing the mobilization of all forces, blanket search for suspected cases, rapid increase in emergency treatment sites, all suspected patients are first centralized isolation, and then organize testing, symptomatic treatment, to ensure that the receivable, a leakproof, strict cross-infection.
。
.
2月2日上午，湖北省新型冠状病毒感染肺炎疫情防控指挥部召开会议。
February 2 morning, Hubei Province, the new coronavirus infection pneumonia command held a meeting.
会议强调，当前，全省防控形势依然极为严峻，要做实做细基层基础工作，坚决按照“四集中”要求，对所有疑似患者集中隔离。
The meeting stressed that, at present, the provincial situation of prevention and control is still extremely serious, to do a detailed basic work, resolutely in accordance with the "four episodes" requirements, all suspected patients in concentrated isolation.
。
.
2月2日下午，湖北省新型冠状病毒感染肺炎疫情防控指挥部召开指挥长会议。
February 2 afternoon, Hubei Province, the new coronavirus infection pneumonia command of the command convened a meeting.
。
.
2月3日，蒋超良到荆州洪湖市检查指导疫情防控工作。
On February 3, Jiang went to Honghu City in Jingzhou to check and direct the epidemic prevention and control work.
。
.
蒋超良称要“深刻反思”。
Jiang said "deep reflection."
。
.
2月3日晚，蒋超良主持召开省委常委会会议暨省新型冠状病毒感染肺炎疫情防控指挥部会议，称要“深刻反思”。
On the evening of February 3, Jiang held a meeting of the Standing Committee of the Provincial Committee and the Provincial Command for the Prevention and Control of Coronavirus Infection Pneumonia, calling for "profound reflection."
。
.
2月4日-9日，蒋超良到武汉市检查督导疫情防控。
February 4-9, Jiang Xiuliang to Wuhan city to inspect and supervise the disease control.
。
.
2月4日，蒋超良到武昌区检查疑似病人集中隔离点安置情况；下午，蒋超良到武汉市检查督导疫情防控工作，要求及时隔离救治疑似及确诊患者。
On February 4, Jiang went to Wuchang District to inspect the resettlement of suspected patients in a concentrated isolation spot. In the afternoon, Jiang went to Wuhan city to inspect and supervise the prevention and control of the epidemic.
。
.
2月5日，蒋超良到武汉市检查督导疫情防控工作，强调要根据疫情变化科学测算全市各项物资需求，提前做好组织供应工作，尤其要保障好医疗一线防护服、N95口罩等需求，绝不允许因防护物资不到位而贻误治疗；下午，蒋超良来到同济医院、协和医院，检查疫情防控工作。
On February 5, Jiang went to Wuhan city to inspect and supervise the work of epidemic prevention and control. He stressed the need to scientifically estimate the requirements of various materials in the city according to the epidemiological changes, to organize supplies well in advance, especially to ensure medical first-line protective clothing and N95 masks.
。
.
2月6日，蒋超良在武汉市督导疫情防控工作，强调要切实以战时状态落细落实各项防控措施。
On February 6, Jiang oversaw the prevention and control of the epidemic in Wuhan city, stressing the need to carefully implement various prevention and control measures in wartime.
。
.
2月7日，蒋超良在武汉市督导疫情防控工作，强调要加快集中隔离点征集及设施改造，继续征集一批酒店、场馆、培训中心等，用于集中收治疑似患者、轻症患者和密切接触人员留观，做好隔离点资源的跨区统筹。
On February 7, Jiang oversaw the prevention and control of the epidemic in Wuhan city, stressing the need to speed up the collection and renovation of centralized quarantine points, and to continue to collect a number of hotels, venues and training centres for the centralized treatment of suspected patients, patients with mild illnesses and close contacts.
。
.
2月8日，蒋超良在武汉市督导疫情防控工作，强调要抓实全面排查工作，确保不落一户、不漏一人，坚决切断传播途径、堵住疫情扩散蔓延；抽调机关干部充实基层排查、防控力量；。
On February 8, Jiang oversaw the prevention and control of the epidemic in Wuhan city, stressing the need to ensure that no household is left behind and no one is missing, to resolutely cut off the way of transmission and stop the spread of the epidemic.
2月12日晚，最后一次主持召开省委常委会会议。
On the evening of 12 February, the Standing Committee of the Provincial Committee was last convened.
。
.
2月8日，蒋超良主持召开省委常委会会议暨省新型冠状病毒感染肺炎疫情防控指挥部会议，传达学习习近平总书记有关重要指示批示精神，研究湖北省贯彻落实措施。
On February 8, Jiang held a meeting of the Standing Committee of the Provincial Committee and the Provincial Command for the Control and Prevention of Coronavirus Infection with Pneumonia, to convey the spirit of the important instructions issued by General Secretary Xi Jinping and to study the implementation measures in Hubei Province.
。
.
2月9日，蒋超良在武汉市督导疫情防控工作，强调要做好全面排查和疑似检测工作。
February 9, Jiang Jiuliang in Wuhan City to supervise the work of disease prevention and control, stressing to do a good job of comprehensive screening and suspected testing.
强化属地、部门、单位、个人“四方责任”，推动机关干部下沉到各街道、社区，充实基层排查、收治力量。
We will strengthen the "quadripartite responsibility" of localities, departments, units and individuals, and promote the sinking of government cadres into streets and communities, so as to strengthen grass-roots screening and treatment.
。
.
2月10日，蒋超良主持召开省委常委会会议及指挥部指挥长会议。
On 10 February, Jiang chaired the meeting of the Standing Committee of the Provincial Committee and the meeting of the Commanders of the Command.
会议强调，重点做好武汉市疫情防控工作。
The meeting stressed that the focus of Wuhan City disease prevention and control work.
确保全市应收尽收患者“清零”、全面排查“清零”、疑似检测“清零”，做到日清日结；做实做细“四类人员”集中收治和隔离工作；。
Ensure that the whole city should receive "zero" patients, a comprehensive screening of "zero", suspected detection "zero," so as to achieve the day-to-day closure; do a detailed "four categories of personnel" centralized admission and isolation work;
2月11日，蒋超良在武汉市督导疫情防控工作，强调要把各级机关干部压到基层去，充实基层排查、收治力量，在防控第一线考察识别干部，以坚强的纪律保障打赢武汉保卫战。
On February 11, Jiang oversaw the prevention and control of the epidemic in Wuhan city, stressing that cadres at all levels should be pushed to the grass-roots level, that the grass-roots investigation and treatment forces should be strengthened, that cadres should be identified on the first line of prevention and control, and that strong disciplinary measures should be taken to win the battle against Wuhan.
。
.
2月12日晚，蒋超良主持召开省委常委会会议暨省新冠肺炎防控指挥部指挥长会议，第一时间传达学习习近平总书记在中央政治局常委会会议分析当前新冠肺炎疫情形势、研究加强防控工作时的重要讲话精神，再学习再领会习近平总书记通过视频会议听取中央指导组和湖北省指挥部工作汇报时的重要讲话精神，研究部署进一步抓好全省疫情防控工作。
On the evening of February 12, President Jiang held a meeting of the Standing Committee of the Provincial Standing Committee and the commander-in-chief of the Xinguan Pneumonia Control and Prevention Command.
。
.
（综合自《湖北日报》、新华社、《人民日报》等公开报道）。
(Synthesis from Hubei Daily, Xinhua News Agency, People's Daily and other public reports).
